{"tid":2249505,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳「試點改革」專家質疑成效","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:22:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca40f7b34777a3f03e49629723e90ad147c04f4","tid":2249505,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201019/VA34BSOMDVFGNNX6CHJBCDIYGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201019%2FVA34BSOMDVFGNNX6CHJBCDIYGA%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZsZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=1414b92b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201019%2FVA34BSOMDVFGNNX6CHJBCDIYGA%2F&h=de05ebbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201019/VA34BSOMDVFGNNX6CHJBCDIYGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n深圳「試點改革」專家質疑成效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DOFxMjsR8LzVvagXCJ6yyBowy1A=/1364x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WZQ7RDWEE5CRVJTAJN7FUIOWYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDOFxMjsR8LzVvagXCJ6yyBowy1A%3D%2F1364x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWZQ7RDWEE5CRVJTAJN7FUIOWYM.jpg&h=0e125889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■深圳在科創等改革方面獲更高自主權。新華社<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。有分析認為，中共高層有意賦予深圳在推動改革上更多自主權，盼藉此增加深圳對外資的吸引力，但中共計劃經濟思維始終未改，故效果成疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有別以往層層審批<br />\n<br />\n國務院上周公佈「深圳綜合改革試點實施方案」（2020-2025），昨舉行記者會公佈40條授權事項清單。金融方面，包括推動具創新引領示範作用的企業發行股票或CDR並在深交所上市，並賦予更大改革自主權，以及加快放開增值電訊業務並逐步取消外資股比等限制。國家發改委副主任寧吉喆強調，這次綜合授權有別以往的「層層審批、逐項審核」，除明確要報批的事項，其他不再逐項報批。深圳市長陳如桂表示，首批授權清單中20多項，需修訂現行法規。<br />\n<br />\n早在2018年有傳中國證監會推進CDR進程，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹指，當局雖聲稱授權事項清單不用「層層審批」，但這並非真正的權力下放。「當局稱『除明確要報批的事項，其他不再逐項報批』，就是留下了一條尾巴，如果它覺得情況失控，地方僭越了中央，它就會把某些事情列為必須報批。」他指這些情況以往在深圳多年都有發生，地方領導都會揣摩上意不會逾越紅線，導致多年來改革停滯不前。<br />\n<br />\n發改委網站/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c0Fh7ilh7yugUSbbJ8FyOOTveyk=/709x649/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BZGOJIGINBXLPVO7LUE7OKBFA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc0Fh7ilh7yugUSbbJ8FyOOTveyk%3D%2F709x649%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BZGOJIGINBXLPVO7LUE7OKBFA.gif&h=2627c639&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fff2dab8c959be795ed4df213bf2e4f0a6a512b8","tid":2249505,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"總之一句講哂<br />\n2020前深圳超越香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaff9ea2175906d5ebdcbc05e1c515f0bbcd3091","tid":2249505,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff2dab8c959be795ed4df213bf2e4f0a6a512b8","tid":2249505,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"總之一句講哂<br />\n2020前深圳超越香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"失業人口?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45961dd058eaeba168a0fead4451b7b449586ba8","tid":2249505,"uid":269137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"即係小學雞最愛嘅既要XXX,亦要OOOpattern啦<br />\n成功就小學雞英明領袖,衰咗就無徹實執行小學雞思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20200713/15/ordersuit-fukuoka/f8/31/j/o1200067514788352197.jpg?caw=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20200713%2F15%2Fordersuit-fukuoka%2Ff8%2F31%2Fj%2Fo1200067514788352197.jpg%3Fcaw%3D800&h=14cdd75b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20185982d58142cbde1df35290f5091afa766a9a